
Hanover Insurance   Where Great People Build Successful CareersAs a dynamic and growing property and casualty insurance company, we offer an innovative and collaborative environment where you’ll gain new experiences and grow your career. We’re searching for the most talented professionals – at every level – to join our team. We offer comprehensive benefits to help you be healthy, build financial security, and balance work and home life. At The Hanover, you’ll enjoy what you do and have the support you need to succeed.  The Hanover Difference    Hanover 2021    Why Insurance    Aligning financial stability and growth  11 of the 30 largest property and casualty companies in the U.S.175Writing business in more than 175 countriesNYSEOne of the oldest member companies on the New York Stock Exchange1One of the fastest growing insurance companies in the industry93%Valued by our customers – 93% of claimants would recommend The Hanover2017Ranked by Forbes as one of America’s 2017 best mid-sized employers506Ranked 506 on the Fortune 1000 listEEO Statement:The Hanover values diversity in the workplace and among our customers. The company provides equal opportunity for employment and promotion to all qualified employees and applicants on the basis of experience, training, education, and ability to do the available work without regard to race, religion, color, age, sex/gender, sexual orientation, national origin, gender identity, disability, marital status, veteran status, genetic information, ancestry or any other status protected by law.  Furthermore, The Hanover Insurance Group is committed to providing an equal opportunity workplace that is free of discrimination and harassment based on national origin, race, color, religion, gender, ancestry, age, sexual orientation, gender identity, disability, marital status, veteran status, genetic information or any other status protected by law. 
   














