At A Glance

The Hanover 
		Insurance Group, Inc. (NYSE: THG), based in Worcester, Mass., is the holding 
		company for a group of insurers that includes The Hanover Insurance Company, 
		also based in Worcester, Citizens Insurance Company of America, headquartered 
		in Howell, Michigan, and Chaucer Holdings PLC, based in London, and their 
		affiliates ... more 
		>>









